high_descs: turn around and walk over to the front of the table immediately to your right and against the wall
grab an apple off of the right side of the table there
turn left and walk over to the fridge on the left side of the room at the end of the room
place the apple inside of the fridge to cool off, then take it back out
turn left and walk forwards over to the kitchen table against the wall on the right side of the room
place the apple down on top of the kitchen table there
anns.task_desc: place a cooled apple down on top of the kitchen table

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the white table on your right.
Pick up the apple off of the white table.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the apple inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and take out the now chilled apple, then close the door.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right to face the white table on you right.
Put the chilled apple on the white table in front of the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple on a white table.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step then turn right and walk three steps then turn right to face the white table.
Pick up the apple that's in front of you near the wall.
Turn left and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the white table that's on your right turning right to face it when you get there.
Put the apple on the edge under the head of lettuce and slightly to the right of it.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple on the table.
